snippet.title: Potatostrike  - Digistrike Gameplay (Beta 0.3.0.0)
snippet.description:
Heyo everyone! Here's a short clip showcasing one of the new unlockable characters, Digistrike.

Digistrike converts all his shields into Rotating Shields that orbit around him. These shields can block up to 10 projectiles, but be careful not to lose them all in a critical moment.

Digistrike and 3 other Potato ships are available in Potatostrike version 0.3.0.0, out now!

If you wish to play the Beta build of Potatostrike, you can find it on itch here:
https://lmg3864.itch.io/potatostrike

Follow me on Mastodon for regular updates on my games:
https://mastodon.gamedev.place/@LMG3864
